                <h2>The Safety, Hygiene, and Post-Care Protocols</h2>

                <p>When puncturing the skin hundreds of thousands of times in a single session, absolute clinical sterility is not optional; it is mandatory. All advanced clinics exclusively utilize sealed, single-use, gamma-irradiated titanium needle cartridges that are opened immediately in front of the patient and destroyed directly after the single session. The face is aggressively disinfected with medical-grade chlorhexidine before the procedure begins. When you trust a professional, you eliminate the catastrophic risk of a massive staph infection that haunts those who attempt this in their dirty bathroom at home.</p>

